Interface HlaTimeStamp

    public interface HlaTimeStamp
extends java.lang.Comparable<HlaTimeStamp>
    A timestamp representing when the message was created.

    This class is Immutable (and therefore ThreadSafe) as defined by Java Concurrency in Practice, see jcip.net.
